HEADWORD: Selfhood
<hw>Self"hood</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Existence as a
separate self, or independent person; conscious personality;
individuality.</def> <rj><au>Bib. Sacra.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

